text: Chetan Sakariya (born 20 August 1998) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Saurashtra in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 22 February 2018. He made his first-class debut for Saurashtra in the 2018–19 Ranji Trophy on 20 November 2018, taking a five-wicket haul in the first innings. He made his Twenty20 debut for Saurashtra in the 2018–19 Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy on 21 February 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Saurashtra cricketers
